span#boardMoves1
  span.comment+moveComment
  span.moveNumber
  span.comment+beforeComment
  a (with move + nag)
  span.comment+afterComment
  div.diagram
  div.variation
    span#boardMoves2+move+var+var1+white
      span.comment+moveComment
      span.moveNumber
      span.comment+beforeComment
      a (with move + nag)
      span.comment+afterComment
      div.diagram
      div.variation

Where:
* span.moveNumber may be empty (or is all the time for black, only when starting as variation)
* span.comment+before and span.comment+after may be empty
* a has to be filled
* div.diagram is only set when needed
* div.variation is added on demand